# Voice Interview UI Redesign — ASCII Wireframes

Wireframes del rediseño propuesto. Cada pantalla muestra **Actual → Rediseño**.

---

## 1. Entry CTA (Company Page)

### Actual
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Company: Acme Corp                                 │
│                                                     │
│  [Edit] [Archive] [🎤 Voice Interview]  ← button    │
│                       outline plano                 │
│                                                     │
│  ┌── InlineDropZone ──────────────────────────────┐ │
│  │  📄 Import locations & waste streams from file │ │
│  │  .xlsx  .pdf  .docx       drop here or browse  │ │
│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│                                                     │
│  Locations (3)                                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Rediseño
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Company: Acme Corp                    [Edit] [···] │
│                                                     │
│  ┌── InlineDropZone ──────────────────────────────┐ │
│  │  ┌──────┐                                      │ │
│  │  │  📄  │  Import locations & waste streams    │ │
│  │  │ blue │  from a spreadsheet or document      │ │
│  │  └──────┘  .xlsx  .pdf  .docx                  │ │
│  │            drop here or browse                  │ │
│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│                                                     │
│  ┌── VoiceInterviewCTA ──── emerald accent ───────┐ │
│  │  ┌──────┐                                      │ │
│  │  │  🎤  │  Capture waste streams from a        │ │
│  │  │green │  voice interview                     │ │
│  │  └──────┘  .mp3  .wav  .m4a                    │ │
│  │            upload a recording                   │ │
│  └──── glass-liquid-subtle rounded-xl ────────────┘ │
│                                                     │
│  Locations (3)                                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

> **Cambio clave**: Voice CTA pasa de un botón `outline` perdido en el header a una card prominente al mismo nivel visual que el file import.

---

## 2. Consent + Upload Modal

### Actual
```
┌── Dialog ─────────────────────────────┐
│  Upload Voice Interview               │
│  Upload-only flow. Audio retained     │
│  180 days, transcript 24 months.      │
│                                       │
│  Audio file                           │
│  [    Choose file    ] No file chosen │
│  Accepted formats: mp3, wav, m4a.     │
│  Max size: 25MB.                      │
│                                       │
│  ☐ I confirm consent was obtained     │
│    for this recording.                │
│                                       │
│           [Cancel]  [📤 Upload]       │
└───────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Rediseño
```
┌── Dialog (520px) ─────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                    │
│  🎤  Voice Interview                               │
│  Capture waste streams from audio                  │
│                                                    │
│  ┌─ Consent ─────────────────────────────────────┐ │
│  │  ☑ I confirm this recording was made with     │ │
│  │    consent of all participants.           ⓘ   │ │
│  └───────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│                                                    │
│  ┌─ Retention Notice ─── muted bg ──────────────┐ │
│  │  🔒 Audio: 180d · Transcript: 24mo ·         │ │
│  │     Audit: 24mo                               │ │
│  └───────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
│                                                    │
│  ┌ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─┐ │
│  ╎               🎵                             ╎ │
│  ╎   Drop audio file here or browse              ╎ │
│  ╎                                               ╎ │
│  ╎   .mp3   .wav   .m4a       Max 25 MB          ╎ │
│  └ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ dashed border ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─ ─┘ │
│                                                    │
│  ▸ Recording from iPhone/iPad?                     │
│  ▸ Recording from Android?                         │
│                                                    │
│  [Cancel]           [Upload & Process] ← emerald   │
│                         (disabled until consent+file)│
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

> **Cambios clave**: Drop zone visual, retention notice en Alert, device helpers colapsibles, formato badges, shadcn Checkbox.

---

## 3. Processing Status (Inline Card)

### Actual
```
┌── Inside Dialog ──────────────────────┐
│  [📤 Processing...]  ← button text    │
│                                       │
│  (polling happens invisibly,          │
│   user sees "Processing..." text      │
│   until review_ready)                 │
└───────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Rediseño
```
┌── Inline card on company page ─────── glass-liquid ─────┐
│                                                          │
│  🎵 interview-acme-site.m4a                         ✕   │
│                                                          │
│  ✅ Uploaded                                             │
│  │                                                       │
│  ⟳ Transcribing audio...   ━━━━━━━━━━░░░░ 45%          │
│  │                                                       │
│  ○ Extracting waste data                                 │
│  │                                                       │
│  ○ Ready for review                                      │
│                                                          │
│  Estimated: ~3 min remaining                             │
│                                                          │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

(on failure:)
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  🎵 interview-acme-site.m4a                         ✕   │
│                                                          │
│  ✅ Uploaded                                             │
│  │                                                       │
│  ❌ Transcription failed                                 │
│     Error: Audio quality too low                         │
│                                           [🔄 Retry]    │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

> **Cambio clave**: Processing sale del dialog y se muestra inline en la página con stepper visual y progreso.

