## Component Map (shadcn)

| Sub-componente | shadcn base | Nuevo archivo |
|---|---|---|
| `VoiceInterviewCTA` | Card + glass-liquid | En [voice-interview-launcher.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-interview-launcher.tsx) |
| Upload drop zone | Div dashed + drag events | En [voice-interview-launcher.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-interview-launcher.tsx) |
| `VoiceProcessingProgress` | Card + custom stepper | `voice-processing-progress.tsx` [NEW] |
| `TranscriptPanel` | ScrollArea + custom segments | `transcript-panel.tsx` [NEW] |
| `AudioPlayer` | Custom `<audio>` + Slider | En `transcript-panel.tsx` |
| `LocationGroupCard` | Card + Collapsible + RadioGroup | `location-group-card.tsx` [NEW] |
| `StreamCard` | Card compact | `stream-card.tsx` [NEW] |
| `VoiceSuccessScreen` | Centered div + animation | `voice-success-screen.tsx` [NEW] |
| `FinalizeBar` | Sticky div | En [voice-review-workspace.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-workspace.tsx) |
